Format: https://www.debian.org/doc/packaging-manuals/copyright-format/1.0/
Upstream-Name: netcode
Upstream-Contact: Glenn Fiedler <glenn@mas-bandwidth.com>
Source: https://github.com/mas-bandwidth/netcode
Files-Excluded: sodium
Comment: The upstream sodium/ directory (a pruned, amalgamated copy of
 libsodium, present so source builds have zero dependencies) is stripped
 from the repacked +ds orig tarball: the Debian package is built with
 -DNETCODE_SYSTEM_SODIUM=ON against the system libsodium, so it receives
 libsodium security updates from the distribution.

